16_54	0.0	If you're the harpooner, you have to have a lot of strength so you can stick it in the whale''.
16_55	0.0	``I really want to take after my ancestors,'' said Eric, one small example of how whaling may infuse a new generation of Makah with the old values that existed before anyone had heard of unemployment or Jim Beam.
