16_60	0.0	It will deliver the coupe de grace once the whale is harpooned, explained Johnson, hefting the weapon.
16_61	0.0	The rifle is one of the concessions to the 20th century made by the Makah.
16_62	0.0	The International Whaling Commission insists on a quick kill.
16_63	0.0	Says McCarty: ``They want us to do a humane kill.
16_64	0.0	That necessitates a quick and efficient method of ushering the whale to the next world.
16_65	0.0	I believe it to be an honorable alteration to a sacred way of life''.
16_66	0.0	But Makah elder Alberta Thompson disapproves not only of the gun, but also of the hunt itself.
