24_29	0.0	The Education Department just created an Indian Teacher Corps to train 1,000 Indian teachers.
24_30	0.125	Currently, most teachers in reservation schools are non-Indian, the turnover rates are extremely high, and many believe the teachers do not understand Indian culture and learning styles.
